  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3959885607" />
    <a title="Sofia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/114413220-sofia"><img alt="Sofia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1607792875p2/114413220.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3959885607?book_show_action=true">Apr 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sofia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sofia" href="/user/show/114413220-sofia">Sofia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780679755333" href="/book/show/505483.A_Raisin_in_the_Sun">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3959885607" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17842537133158744984">The characters were two-dimensional and a bit too straightforward for my liking, having clear dreams and ambitions and very little depth. The themes were more surface-level than I was expecting, and I wished the book would have taken more time discussing civil rights, as it was mostly glossed over. The character development could be interesting at times, however.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


